### Test Email Verification OTP Flow

### 1. Request Registration OTP
POST http://localhost:3000/auth/request-registration-otp
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "1163301010101@rmutt.ac.th"
}

### 2. Verify Registration OTP
POST http://localhost:3000/auth/verify-registration-otp
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "1163301010101@rmutt.ac.th",
  "otp": "123456"
}

### 3. Test with invalid email domain (should fail)
POST http://localhost:3000/auth/request-registration-otp
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "test@gmail.com"
}

### 4. Test with invalid OTP (should fail)
POST http://localhost:3000/auth/verify-registration-otp
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "1163301010101@rmutt.ac.th",
  "otp": "000000"
}
